CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 22, 1940, pg. 8 reads: "The Bride Cuts The Cake - Mrs. William L. Dugas, the former Miss Henri Avant, cuts the cake, while her groom looks on. The couple was wed last Saturday evening at the bride's home in Frankstown avenue, Pittsburgh.  The groom hails from Milwaukee. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Bride Henri Avant Dugas and groom William L. Dugas, standing in home of Mr. and Mrs. J. D. Avant of 8106 Frankstown Avenue
